Origin and attribution
----------------------

This repository began as a fork of the MIT-licensed GoInk project and has
since been renamed and substantially rebuilt as Novelist, a .NET 10 +
Photino.NET desktop app with a React/Vite frontend.

The active Novelist implementation lives under src/, frontend/src/, and tests/.
The retired Go/Wails product path is not part of the active implementation.
Legacy GoInk names such as goink.md and ~/.goink may still appear in source
code as user-data compatibility and migration paths.

The upstream GoInk project later changed its license. Novelist does not merge
post-relicense upstream code and remains distributed under the MIT License for
the code in this repository.

